title: Season 7 Time Capsule (Part 2)
description: Join host Neil Tyson for Season 7’s final episode as he revisits our fan’s favorite Cosmic Queries shows. Along with Chuck Nice, Eugene Mirman, Iliza Shlesinger, and guests, Neil answers questions about aliens, the multiverse, black holes, war, and more.
author: feed@startalkradio.net (Neil deGrasse Tyson)
